content: Hello! Under State Engagement, the only state I see is Mississippi. Is there a channel for each state?
There is, but if you want to campaign locally in more than one, let me know and I can add a few others so you can have access.
You have both MA and MS now, if you don't want MS i can remove it.
Yes, I love MS but I won't be campaigning there this time around. Thank you very much!
Hi - I have the same question as LeftyLucy. I’m from MA but I was assigned to the @MS role and not the @MA role. Can someone please add me to @MA and remove me from @MS?
Hi there, similar question! Can I be added to Connecticut as well as New York?
Hi Grace you have CT and NY, you can choose as many as you want in the Channels and Roles at the top of the server menu.
Oh, I see! Thank you so much
